---
// About section - Industrial heritage meets modern cocktail bar
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#1a1a1a] relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle background accent -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full opacity-5 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#b87333] to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <!-- Section Label -->
        <span class="text-[#b87333] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sm font-medium mb-4 block">
          Our Story
        </span>

        <!-- Heading -->
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl text-[#f5f5dc] mb-8 leading-tight">
          Welcome to<br />
          <span class="text-[#b87333]">The Loft</span>
        </h2>

        <!-- Decorative Line -->
        <div class="w-20 h-px bg-[#b87333] mb-8"></div>

        <!-- Description -->
        <div class="space-y-6 text-[#f5f5dc]/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Standing over the historic waterways of the <strong class="text-[#f5f5dc] font-medium">River Don</strong>,
            The Loft overlooks the iconic smelting pot of Sheffield's industrial past. Our characterful open space
            features <strong class="text-[#f5f5dc] font-medium">exposed brick walls</strong>, high ceilings with
            original <strong class="text-[#f5f5dc] font-medium">oak beams</strong>, and a bespoke interior.
          </p>

          <p>
            With our own <strong class="text-[#f5f5dc] font-medium">beer and gin bar</strong>, we offer everything
            from perfectly poured pints to expertly crafted cocktails. The Loft provides a unique setting for
            those seeking something different in the heart of <strong class="text-[#f5f5dc] font-medium">Kelham Island</strong>.
          </p>

          <p>
            Our flexible space is perfect for <strong class="text-[#f5f5dc] font-medium">private hire</strong> -
            from corporate events and networking to parties and private dining. DM us on Instagram to discuss
            your event.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Accent Feature -->
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 border border-[#b87333] rotate-45 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-[#b87333] rotate-45"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-[#b87333] font-serif text-xl italic">
              "Sheffield's hidden gem on the waterways"
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Visual Element -->
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Placeholder for image - atmospheric gradient box -->
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2a1f1a] via-[#1a1a1a] to-[#2a1f1a] rounded-sm overflow-hidden relative">
            <!-- Decorative overlays -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#b87333]/10 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-4 border border-[#b87333]/20"></div>

            <!-- Placeholder content -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="font-serif text-6xl text-[#b87333]/30 mb-2">L</div>
                <p class="text-[#f5f5dc]/30 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Image Coming Soon</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative corner accents -->
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#b87333]"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-[#b87333]"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
